; Regression test for issue #595: Add a value expression function to round non-commoditized amounts (BZ#595)
; https://github.com/ledger/ledger/issues/595
; The roundto(value, n) function was requested to round non-commoditized amounts.
; Tests confirm the function is implemented and works correctly.

2024/01/01 Test rounding
    Expenses:Food    10.333
    Assets:Cash     -10.333

test reg --format "%(roundto(amount, 2))\n"
10.33
-10.33
end test
